    "id": "重排链表",
    "title": "重排链表",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "topic": "链表",
    "sourceTopic": "链表相关",
    "leetcode": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/reorder-list/",
    "description": "给定一个单链表 `L` 的头节点 `head` ，单链表 `L` 表示为：\n输入：head = [1,2,3,4]\n输出：[1,4,2,3]\n输入：head = [1,2,3,4,5]",
    "ideaMarkdown": "重排链表这道题综合性比较强，需要用找中间结点、反转链表、拼接链表操作。代码不是很难写。贴一张`claude`生成的图直观看一下代码逻辑。",
    "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    void reorderList(ListNode* head) {\n        // 找到中间结点\n        ListNode* low = head;\n        ListNode* fast = head;\n        while (fast != nullptr && fast->next != nullptr)\n        {\n            low = low->next;\n            fast = fast->next->next;\n        }\n        // 断开左右两部分 人为让左半部分大于等于右边部分的长度。\n        ListNode* start = low->next;\n        low->next = nullptr;\n        // 【low+1，end】链表反转\n        ListNode* pre = nullptr;\n        ListNode* cur = start;\n        ListNode* nxt = nullptr;\n        while(cur != nullptr)\n        {\n            nxt = cur->next;\n            cur->next = pre;\n            pre = cur;\n            cur = nxt;\n        }\n        //交替拼接链表\n        ListNode* p1 = head;\n        ListNode* p2 = pre;       \n        while(p2 != nullptr)//因为左半部分长度大于等于右半部分，所以肯定是右半部分先结束。\n        {\n           ListNode* temp1 = p1->next;\n           ListNode* temp2 = p2->next;\n           p1->next = p2;\n           p2->next = temp1;\n           p1 = temp1;\n           p2 = temp2;\n        }\n    }\n};",
    "noteMarkdown": "> 给定一个单链表 `L` 的头节点 `head` ，单链表 `L` 表示为：\n>\n> ```\n> L0 → L1 → … → Ln - 1 → Ln\n> ```\n>\n> 请将其重新排列后变为：\n>\n> ```\n> L0 → Ln → L1 → Ln - 1 → L2 → Ln - 2 → …\n> ```\n>\n> 不能只是单纯的改变节点内部的值，而是需要实际的进行节点交换。\n>\n> **示例 1：**\n>\n> ![img](https://pic.leetcode.cn/1626420311-PkUiGI-image.png)\n>\n> ```\n> 输入：head = [1,2,3,4]\n> 输出：[1,4,2,3]\n> ```\n>\n> **示例 2：**\n>\n> ![img](https://pic.leetcode.cn/1626420320-YUiulT-image.png)\n>\n> ```\n> 输入：head = [1,2,3,4,5]\n> 输出：[1,5,2,4,3]\n> ```\n>\n> **提示：**\n>\n> - 链表的长度范围为 `[1, 5 * 104]`\n> - `1 <= node.val <= 1000`\n\n思路：重排链表这道题综合性比较强，需要用找中间结点、反转链表、拼接链表操作。代码不是很难写。贴一张`claude`生成的图直观看一下代码逻辑。\n\n<img src=\"https://xubenshan-pic.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/%E9%87%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8.png\" alt=\"重排链表\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n\n代码：\n\n```cpp\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    void reorderList(ListNode* head) {\n        // 找到中间结点\n        ListNode* low = head;\n        ListNode* fast = head;\n        while (fast != nullptr && fast->next != nullptr)\n        {\n            low = low->next;\n            fast = fast->next->next;\n        }\n        // 断开左右两部分 人为让左半部分大于等于右边部分的长度。\n        ListNode* start = low->next;\n        low->next = nullptr;\n        // 【low+1，end】链表反转\n        ListNode* pre = nullptr;\n        ListNode* cur = start;\n        ListNode* nxt = nullptr;\n        while(cur != nullptr)\n        {\n            nxt = cur->next;\n            cur->next = pre;\n            pre = cur;\n            cur = nxt;\n        }\n        //交替拼接链表\n        ListNode* p1 = head;\n        ListNode* p2 = pre;       \n        while(p2 != nullptr)//因为左半部分长度大于等于右半部分，所以肯定是右半部分先结束。\n        {\n           ListNode* temp1 = p1->next;\n           ListNode* temp2 = p2->next;\n           p1->next = p2;\n           p2->next = temp1;\n           p1 = temp1;\n           p2 = temp2;\n        }\n    }\n};\n\n```",
    "codeBlocks": [
      "class Solution {\npublic:\n    void reorderList(ListNode* head) {\n        // 找到中间结点\n        ListNode* low = head;\n        ListNode* fast = head;\n        while (fast != nullptr && fast->next != nullptr)\n        {\n            low = low->next;\n            fast = fast->next->next;\n        }\n        // 断开左右两部分 人为让左半部分大于等于右边部分的长度。\n        ListNode* start = low->next;\n        low->next = nullptr;\n        // 【low+1，end】链表反转\n        ListNode* pre = nullptr;\n        ListNode* cur = start;\n        ListNode* nxt = nullptr;\n        while(cur != nullptr)\n        {\n            nxt = cur->next;\n            cur->next = pre;\n            pre = cur;\n            cur = nxt;\n        }\n        //交替拼接链表\n        ListNode* p1 = head;\n        ListNode* p2 = pre;       \n        while(p2 != nullptr)//因为左半部分长度大于等于右半部分，所以肯定是右半部分先结束。\n        {\n           ListNode* temp1 = p1->next;\n           ListNode* temp2 = p2->next;\n           p1->next = p2;\n           p2->next = temp1;\n           p1 = temp1;\n           p2 = temp2;\n        }\n    }\n};"
    ]
