    "leetcode": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/binary-tree-zigzag-level-order-traversal/",
    "description": "给你二叉树的根节点 `root` ，返回其节点值的 **锯齿形层序遍历** 。（即先从左往右，再从右往左进行下一层遍历，以此类推，层与层之间交替进行）。\n输入：root = [3,9,20,null,null,15,7]\n输出：[[3],[20,9],[15,7]]",
    "ideaMarkdown": "这道题看起来复杂，其实不复杂。如何实现锯齿形遍历呢，本质上就是偶数层的时候将遍历得到的节点反转一下。弄清楚本质，这道题的代码就不难写了。",
    "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<vector<int>> zigzagLevelOrder(TreeNode* root) {\n        vector<vector<int>> ans;\n        if (root == nullptr) return ans;\n        queue<TreeNode*> q;\n        q.push(root);\n        vector<int> val;\n        bool bit = false; //代表当前是不是偶数层\n        while(!q.empty())\n        {\n            val = {};\n            int size = q.size();\n            for (int i = 0; i < size; i++)\n            {\n                TreeNode* node = q.front();\n                q.pop();\n                if (node->left) q.push(node->left);\n                if (node->right) q.push(node->right);\n                val.push_back(node->val);\n            }\n            //偶数层val数组反转一下\n            if (bit) reverse(val.begin(), val.end());\n            ans.push_back(val);\n            bit = !bit;// ~bit 是按位取反 !bit 才是逻辑取反\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};",
